<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.4.9">
<l>cēya ṉeṉṟumi ka<supplied>p</supplied>peri  yaṉuṇṇēr maiyaṉāyavim</l>
<l>māyai yāru maṟiyā vakaiyā ṉiṭameṉparāl</l>
<l>vēyiṉ muttum maṇiyuṅ koṇarntārp puṉaṟkāviri</l>
<l>yāya poṉmā matiḷcūḻn taḻakār teṉṉaraṅkamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They truly say that the place of the one with a nature,</l>
<l rend="indent">which is incomprehensible by anyone,</l>
<l>That is this illusion that he is remote [and that] he is always very great,</l>
<l rend="indent">[yet] he is of subtle minuteness,</l>
<l>Is Araṅkam of the South, filled with beauty, with large walls</l>
<l rend="indent">covered with fine gold encircling [it],</l>
<l>[And] the Kāviri, its full waters bringing jewels and bamboo pearls.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
